Subject: [PATCH 17/17] ima: Also allow MEASURE policy rules in the IMA
 namespace

Also allow MEASURE policy rules in the IMA namespace now.

Signed-off-by: Stefan Berger <stefanb@linux.ibm.com>
---
 security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c b/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
index 6c62ba490310..5435cc340d63 100644
--- a/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
+++ b/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
@@ -1797,7 +1797,6 @@ static int ima_parse_rule(struct ima_namespace *ns,
 		/* IMA namespace only accepts AUDIT rules */
 		if (ns != &init_ima_ns) {
 			switch (entry->action) {
-			case MEASURE:
 			case APPRAISE:
 			case HASH:
 				result = -EINVAL;
